body:
jquery could help out.
basically this scripts checks the event fired by a keystroke. if the keystroke was alt +, it loops over all files and checks if the name starts with a dot. if so, .toggle() is invoked, toggling visibility of this element in the filelist.
```javascript
$(document).ready(function()
{
	$(window).keydown(function(event) { 
		//+ fires event 107
		if (event.altkey && event.which === 107) {
			//get all the table rows with files and loop (each)
			$('#filelist [data-file^="."]').each(function(){
				$(this).toggle();
			});
		} 

	});

});
```

